{"type":"text","timestamp":1775907938488,"sessionID":"ses_283a8f1b8ffeuMAM0MLnXzGmgw","part":{"id":"prt_d7c5c64bd001kvXqlZ7wXpPqow","messageID":"msg_d7c5c4d9e001KA9d9XivYERuDP","sessionID":"ses_283a8f1b8ffeuMAM0MLnXzGmgw","type":"text","text":"I've written the `delta-spec.md` file for AR-029 — SDK HTTP 底层客户端. The specification includes:\n\n## Summary\n\n**File:** `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-029/delta-spec.md`\n\n**Content Overview:**\n\n### Requirements with GIVEN/WHEN/THEN Scenarios:\n\n1. **HTTP Session Factory** (`create_session` utility)\n   - Default pool settings (10 connections)\n   - Custom pool configuration\n   - Connection reuse\n\n2. **Control Plane HTTP Client** (`ControlPlaneClient`)\n   - Create session POST request with JSON body\n   - Delete session with 404 idempotency\n   - Workload Manager URL resolution from env\n   - Auth token resolution from service account file\n   - Timeout tuple handling `(connect_timeout, timeout)`\n\n3. **Code Interpreter Data Plane HTTP Client** (`CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient`)\n   - Base URL construction from router URL\n   - Execute command POST with timeout buffer (+2.0s)\n   - Write file with base64 encoding\n   - Upload file multipart with explicit session header\n   - Download file with streaming\n   - List files with query parameters\n   - Session header on all requests\n\n4. **Agent Runtime Data Plane HTTP Client** (`AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient`)\n   - Base URL construction\n   - Bootstrap session ID from GET response header\n   - Invoke POST with session header and JSON payload\n   - Timeout tuple configuration\n   - `SESSION_HEADER` constant\n\n5. **Timeout Behavior**\n   - Default timeouts (connect: 5.0s, read: 120s)\n   - Per-request override\n   - Constructor override\n\n6. **Session Header Management**\n   - Consistent `x-agentcube-session-id` header usage\n   - Default headers vs explicit headers\n\n7. **Connection Pool Configuration**\n   - Default pool settings (10/10)\n   - Custom pool configuration\n\n### Additional Sections:\n- **Interface:** Method signatures for all clients\n- **Behavior:** HTTP request flow and timeout hierarchy\n- **Dependencies:** requests, PyJWT, cryptography\n- **File Index:** All implementation files\n- **Testing:** Unit test scenarios\n- **Deliverables:** Complete file list","time":{"start":1775907938485,"end":1775907938485}}}
